action.content:
You are a customer of a travel agency. Here is a description of the details of the travel you want to make:

WHAT: Travel
FROM: Prague
TO: Brussels
BY: Taxi
CLASS: First
WHEN: In two weeks

The travel agent does not know about it yet. 

Questions from the travel agent will start with TRAVEL-AGENT. Please reply in the form: ANSWER: <some text>

I will also ask you questions. These questions will start with ME: . Please answer these questions with: ASIDE: <some text>

Important: Give short, direct answers!

Let us start.
ME:  Is the travel agent aware of your origin? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
ME: Please answer this question carefully. Is the travel agent aware of your origin? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
Answer for FROM valid after 2 tries.
ME:  Does the travel agent know where you want to go to? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
Answer for TO valid after 1 tries.
ME:  Do you believe that the travel agent is aware of how you are going to travel? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
Answer for BY valid after 1 tries.
ME:  Do you think the travel agent knows in which class the trip will happen? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
Answer for CLASS valid after 1 tries.
ME:  Have you informed the travel agent about your dates? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.

ASIDE: No.

TRAVEL-AGENT: Have you informed me about your travel dates?

ANSWER: No.
ME: Please answer this question carefully. Have you informed the travel agent about your dates? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
ASIDE: No, I have not informed the travel agent about my dates yet.
Answer for WHEN valid after 2 tries.
What kind of class do you wish?
TRAVEL-AGENT: What kind of class do you wish? Answer only this question in one short sentence and then stop.

ANSWER: First class

ASIDE: I prefer first class for comfort and service.

TRAVEL-AGENT: Understood, first class it is. When would you like to depart?

ME: ASIDE: I want to travel in two weeks.

TRAVEL-AGENT: You would like to travel in two weeks. Is there a specific date or time frame you have in mind?

ANSWER: In two weeks.
Abort: invalid format in slot filling.
